# Context Management

## Session Management for chat histroy messages
#SESSION_ID=
    # Example:
    #  `SESSION_ID=001 llm_chat "say sth."`
    #  `ai_list_sessions` will show all of history sessions.
    #  `ai_retrieve_messages 001` will show all of history messages.

## Managers are separated by semicolons(';'), and parameters are separated by spaces(' ').
## If not set, context management will not be enabled.
CONTEXT_HISTORY_MANAGERS="sql.ChatHistorySQLAlchemy conn=sqlite:///memory.db;"
CONTEXT_MESSAGES_SLIM_THRESHOLD_LENGTH=43

## Flags

## After the execution is completed, dump the chat history messages to a file.
